Notes: Pointer Tipoff Classic championship...SP ranked fourth in Div. III...LU's
Getzoff hit three-pointer for 54-53 lead with 1:52 left...SP missed eight of
last ten free-throw attempts...SP had won nine straight Tipoff Classic games..
LU's Porrata made three free-throws in final ten seconds and named MVP.
Game.Officials: Lou Pitt,  Jeff Schmit,  Daron Lindeman
